t is an asymptotic series in $\\epsilon$\nthat may be truncated appropriately considering the physical properties of the\nregarded system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2013 11:48:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 13:37:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-30"}
