itational redshifts amount up to 0.7\nkm/s and dominate convective blueshifts for dwarfs, but become much weaker for\ngiants.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2013 14:41:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
